data<-data %>%
  rowwise() %>%
  mutate("gsd"=get_GSD(Altitude = alt_above_ground))

#cm/px

plot_data<-data %>% 
  select(id,gsd)
plot_data %>% 
  group_by(id) %>% 
  summarise(mean=mean(gsd, na.rm = TRUE), sd=sd(gsd, na.rm = TRUE))
